query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('battery',
'bluetooth',
'bsod',
'encryption',
'firewall',
'lenovo-laptop',
'linux-mint',
'microsoft-outlook-2010',
'sata',
'software-rec',
'sync',
'taskbar',
'thinkpad',
'windows-registry')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('superuser')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1 group by t1.name;
